            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627987914464-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the<strong> tomato stock</strong> to the pan with the vegetables and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened – these are your <strong>Mediterranean vegetables</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
